{"id":87570,"title":"Initial assessment and fluid resuscitation of burn patients.","abstract":"For the physician or surgeon practicing outside the confines of a burn center, initial assessment and fluid resuscitation will encompass most of his or her exposure to patients with severe burns. The importance of this phase of care should not be underestimated. This article provides a review of how to perform initial resuscitation of patients with significant burns and/or inhalation injury, while arranging for transfer to a regional burn center. ","date":"2014-08-02","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25085085","annotations":[{"name":"Injury","weight":0.787846,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Injury"},{"name":"Physician","weight":0.617472,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physician"},{"name":"Cardiopulmonary resuscitation","weight":0.608877,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardiopulmonary_resuscitation"},{"name":"Hypothermia","weight":0.599967,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypothermia"},{"name":"Burn","weight":0.460249,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burn"},{"name":"Fluid","weight":0.37733,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fluid"},{"name":"Fluid replacement","weight":0.215427,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fluid_replacement"},{"name":"Inhalation","weight":0.105637,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inhalation"},{"name":"Surgeon","weight":0.0537772,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgeon"},{"name":"Arrangement","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arrangement"},{"name":"Psychological evaluation","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychological_evaluation"},{"name":"Burn center","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burn_center"},{"name":"Phase (matter)","weight":0.014